Class ConnectedExternalIdentifiers

org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworkservices.ocf.metadatamanagement.client.ConnectedExternalIdentifiers
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Iterator<ExternalIdentifier>
public class ConnectedExternalIdentifiers extends ExternalIdentifiers
ConnectedExternalIdentifiers provides the open metadata concrete implementation of the Open Connector Framework (OCF) ExternalIdentifiers abstract class. Its role is to query the property servers (metadata repository cohort) to extract external identifiers related to the connected asset.
